Records mouse & keyboard inputs to repeat any number of times
Recording will be saved in a txt file & will auto load when the program launches again next time.


NOTE: Only allows for 1 recorded file at a time, creating a new recording will overwrite the first one.



To record:
- Click record and do anything needed. 
- Click the esc key to stop recording

To play:
- Enter out how many times you want your macro to repeat (default is 1)
- Click play


